# Astro Component Guidelines

## Component Structure
- Use TypeScript in frontmatter for type safety
- Import types from `astro:content` for content collections
- Use path aliases: `@/components/`, `@/layouts/`, etc.

## Styling Approach
- **Primary**: Use DaisyUI classes for component styling
- **Secondary**: Use Tailwind CSS only when DaisyUI doesn't provide needed styles
- Custom theme "grobles" is available with green-tinted color scheme

## Key Components
- [BaseHead.astro](mdc:src/components/BaseHead.astro) - SEO and meta tags
- [Header.astro](mdc:src/components/Header.astro) - Site navigation
- [Footer.astro](mdc:src/components/Footer.astro) - Site footer
- [FormattedDate.astro](mdc:src/components/FormattedDate.astro) - Date formatting

## Layout Components
- [BlogPost.astro](mdc:src/layouts/BlogPost.astro) - Blog post layout with hero images
- [Page.astro](mdc:src/layouts/Page.astro) - General page layout

## Best Practices
- Use `Image` component from `astro:assets` for optimized images
- Leverage content collections for type-safe blog posts
- Follow the established component naming and structure patterns